  "title": "Security Engineer (2-Year Contract)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Duties &amp; Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Involve in the project or lead the project related with IT infrastructure and data centre whenever required</li>\n  <li>Perform Installation, Implementation, Configuration and testing of system/storage equipment &amp; setup</li>\n  <li>Perform OS hardening, patching and updating on servers/VM</li>\n  <li>Perform installation &amp; configuration on storage (SAN and NAS)</li>\n  <li>Plan for migration, document and execute the migration plan</li>\n  <li>Develop implementation plan, migration plan and acceptance test plan for the project.</li>\n  <li>Conduct acceptance test with users and address the testing findings/issues</li>\n  <li>Provide system architecture design and planning for new IT infrastructure deployments in both hosted and cloud environments</li>\n  <li>Support maintenance team in difficult or chronic problems, escalate the issue to vendor, identifying the root cause and preventive measures</li>\n  <li>Support presales team on infrastructure solutioning in bids</li>\n  <li>Review the project change request and carry out the integration/implementation</li>\n  <li>Work closely with Project Managers in planning the implementation tasks</li>\n  <li>Support VAPT and SSAT requirements</li>\n  <li>Develop As-built documentation for handover</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Skills &amp; Experience</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum Diploma in Computer Science or IT related studies</li>\n  <li>Minimum 7 years’ experience in IT industry with at least 5 years in systems &amp; security arena</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of networking and IP/TCP protocol</li>\n  <li>In-depth knowledge in network and systems security issues</li>\n  <li>Hands-on experience in security-related tasks such as OS tightening, patching and updating, virus scanning will be an added advantage.</li>\n  <li>In-depth knowledge on network and systems security issues and ability to offer advisories and troubleshooting support.</li>\n  <li>In-depth knowledge on enterprise backup, virtualization and storage</li>\n  <li>IT Certification in system &amp; storage, network, database, virtualization, cloud technologies</li>\n  <li>Good communication skills and positive working attitude</li>\n</ul>",
